    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "MOSQUITO MASHER",
        "Description": "Welcome agent, the presence of double agents has increased, Whittleton Creek is no longer as safe as it used to be. Double agents are all over the place like mosquitos. People live day to day in fear of going out and being spied on in their own neighborhood. Double agents must be exterminated. This contract was created by members of the HITMAN community known as josthin and Thornicroft.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as josthin and Thornicroft.",
